  "page": "Fall of Raventree Hall",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Fall of Raventree Hall</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\nlate <a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a> or early <a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Raventree Hall\">Raventree Hall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> victory<br />Occupation of <a href=\"/index.php/Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Raventree Hall\">Raventree Hall</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/32px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/48px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/64px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:<br />\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/32px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/48px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/64px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Tywin_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Tywin-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/32px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/48px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/64px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/20px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/40px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/20px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/40px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/20px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/40px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>fall of Raventree Hall</b> is part of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> invasion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Fall_of_Raventree_Hall\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Fall of Raventree Hall</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Raventree_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Mummer%27s_Ford\" title=\"Battle at the Mummer&#39;s Ford\">battle at the Mummer's Ford</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> leads his 20,000 men northeast toward the <a href=\"/index.php/Ruby_ford\" title=\"Ruby ford\">ruby ford</a>. Tywin's son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>, captures Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> in a <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Battle under the walls of Riverrun\">battle under the walls of Riverrun</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Blackwood\" title=\"Tytos Blackwood\">Tytos Blackwood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Raventree_Hall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord of Raventree Hall\">Lord of Raventree Hall</a>, holds <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> while it is besieged by Jaime.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Fall_of_Raventree_Hall\">Fall of Raventree Hall</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Raventree_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Fall of Raventree Hall\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Without Lord Tytos to lead the defense, <a href=\"/index.php/Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Raventree Hall\">Raventree Hall</a> falls to the army of Tywin and his brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Tywin's host goes on to capture <a href=\"/index.php/Yielding_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Yielding of Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Darry\" title=\"Capture of Darry\">Darry</a>, and sack <a href=\"/index.php/First_sack_of_Maidenpool\" title=\"First sack of Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>, whilst Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> is deployed to burn <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Pinkmaiden_Castle\" title=\"Burning of Pinkmaiden Castle\">Pinkmaiden</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Burning of Stone Hedge\">Stone Hedge</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Raventree_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tywin leaves Raventree under the control of a Lannister garrison. Later, after <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>'s victories at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_Whispering_Wood\" title=\"Battle in the Whispering Wood\">Whispering Wood</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Camps\" title=\"Battle of the Camps\">Battle of the Camps</a> and Tywin's retreat to <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>, Raventree Hall is <a href=\"/index.php/Liberation_of_Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Liberation of Raventree Hall\">liberated</a> by Lord Tytos.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Raventree_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Tywin-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Tywin_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Brax\" title=\"House Brax\">Brax</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\">Clegane</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Crakehall\" title=\"House Crakehall\">Crakehall</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lefford\" title=\"House Lefford\">Lefford</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lydden\" title=\"House Lydden\">Lydden</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Marbrand\" title=\"House Marbrand\">Marbrand</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Payne\" title=\"House Payne\">Payne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Serrett\" title=\"House Serrett\">Serrett</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Swyft\" title=\"House Swyft\">Swyft</a> are not directly mentioned at Raventree. However, as men from these houses are part of <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>'s host in the riverlands, they may be present at Raventree.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Raventree_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Events#The_War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Events\">War of the Five Kings</a> calculations.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, Tyrion VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_48\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 48\">Chapter 48</a>, Jaime I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_7\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 7\">Chapter 7</a>, Catelyn I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;